---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ApopTosis AI — STEM + LANG = SAFE">
  <section class="hero bg-gradient-to-b from-prime-blue to-black min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flux-ring absolute inset-0 m-auto w-96 h-96 opacity-30">
      <div class="stem">STEM</div>
      <div class="safe">SAFE</div>
      <div class="lang">LANG</div>
      <div class="center-symbol">π</div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center z-10 px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-garamond text-prime-gold mb-8 leading-tight">
        Not to win.<br>To cooperate.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-3xl mb-8 font-bold">STEM + LANG = SAFE</p>
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
        Like a garden where roots and branches grow in symbiosis, AI extends human intent — not replaces it. 
        <span class="text-prime-gold">1/2 your intent + 1/2 our precision = partnership that protects.</span>
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8 text-lg">
        <div class="p-6 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-prime-gold mb-3 font-bold text-xl">STEM (Expansion)</p>
          <p class="mb-2">Like sunlight that nurtures growth — Science and Mathematics open paths to <span class="text-prime-gold">Equality</span> and <span class="text-prime-gold">Freedom</span>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-prime-gold mb-3 font-bold text-xl">LANG (Contraction)</p>
          <p class="mb-2">Like soil that anchors roots — Norms and Engineering ensure <span class="text-prime-gold">Security</span> and <span class="text-prime-gold">Accountability</span>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        In the balance between expansion and contraction, we find SAFE: a future where innovation grows without choking freedom, 
        where cooperation becomes as natural as cells renewing.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-8 flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/ethics" class="bg-prime-gold text-prime-blue px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-opacity-80 transition-colors">Explore Ethics</a>
        <a href="/primeflux" class="border-2 border-prime-gold text-prime-gold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-prime-gold hover:text-prime-blue transition-colors">PrimeFlux Vision</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-16 bg-prime-blue text-center">
    <p class="text-2xl font-garamond italic text-prime-gold max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      This is not to win.<br>This is to cooperate.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
